{"id":124950,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/图辑：上海十万人自发悼念火灾死者/","date":"2010-11-23T11:13:20Z","modified":"2010-11-23T11:13:20Z","title":"图辑：上海十万人自发悼念火灾死者","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h2>图辑：上海十万人自发悼念胶州路火灾死难者</h2>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122034215_shanghai01_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"前往火灾现场吊唁的上海市民\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122034215_shanghai01_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>星期日（11月21日）是上海胶州路火灾死难者的“头七”，大约十万上海民众前往火灾现场向死难者表达悼念之情。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122033953_shanghai02_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"前往火灾现场吊唁的上海市民\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122033953_shanghai02_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>到现场吊唁的民众沉默排队等待，队伍绵延数百米，他们中除上海人外，也有从外地专程前来吊唁的人士。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122034833_shanghai03_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"前往火灾现场吊唁的上海市民向死者献花\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122034833_shanghai03_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>民众向火灾死难者献花，白色和黄色的菊花是现场最常见的花朵。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122040408_shanghai04_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"火灾现场参加自发悼念活动的青年人手持印有上海不哭泣字样的宣传单\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122040408_shanghai04_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>火灾现场参加自发悼念活动的青年人手持印有“上海不哭泣”和“沉痛悼念胶州路大火的遇难同胞”字样的宣传单</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122041019_shanghai05_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"到火灾现场悼念死者的民众\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122041019_shanghai05_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>不少前来吊唁的民众情绪悲痛。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122043535_shanghai06_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"现场维持秩序的警察\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122043535_shanghai06_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>当局出动大批警察维持秩序，也有志愿者自发协助。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122045221_shanghai07_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"吊唁者为死难者祈祷\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/22/101122045221_shanghai07_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>夜晚，有吊唁者用蜡烛拼出心型和11.15字样，并为死难者祈祷。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/v3L7poVZsalQFVEcOLj6BmWebYM/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/v3L7poVZsalQFVEcOLj6BmWebYM/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/v3L7poVZsalQFVEcOLj6BmWebYM/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/v3L7poVZsalQFVEcOLj6BmWebYM/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/BBC/China/~4/JKN1I5k18js\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/11/101122_shanghai_fire_mourning.shtml\" title=\"图辑：上海十万人自发悼念火灾死者\">图辑：上海十万人自发悼念火灾死者</a></p>\n","author":138,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}